marketing: Shell Rotella SD Grease is a high performance high temperature grease for vehicle and equipment lubrication. Formulated with moly solid lubricant (molybdenum disulfide), Shell Rotella SD Grease is designed for lubrication of demanding applications in vehicles and equipment including high shock loads where rapid starts and stops may occur such as chassis points, sliding pins, trailer hitches, and axle splines where shock loading is possible.
